1. *Sanjala* sam da sam na plaži. (I dreamed that I was at the beach.)
2. Upravo sam *sanjala* najneobičniji san. (I just had the most unusual dream.)
3. Ona je sinoć *sanjala* svog pokojnog dedu. (She dreamed of her late grandfather last night.)
4. Nisam *sanjala* ništa zanimljivo poslednjih dana. (I haven't dreamt anything interesting lately.)
5. *Sanjala* sam da sam zakasnila na avion. (I dreamt that I missed my flight.)
6. Moja sestra često *sanja* o putovanjima. (My sister often dreams about traveling.)
7. Kada sam se probudila, setila sam se svega što sam *sanjala*. (When I woke up, I remembered everything I had dreamed.)
8. *Sanjala sam* te noćas. (I dreamed about you last night.)
9. Pre nego što sam legla da spavam, poželela sam da *sanjam* o nečemu lepom. (Before I went to bed, I wished to dream about something nice.)
10. Bila sam toliko umorna da nisam mogla ni da *sanjam* jasno. (I was so tired that I couldn't dream clearly.)